  "description": "Cisternlight Sleeping Niche is a compact bedroom partitioned by translucent slagglass panels that preserve Auroral Sump House’s strict bands of navigational color. A low sleeping platform is set into a facet-tiled recess, its edges sealed with dust-slick grout that resists the house’s electrostatic glass fallouts. Narrow lens-shelves inset along the wall capture spill from the central cistern and refract it into calibrated twilight bars across the ceiling. A grounded gutter line runs beneath the sill, tying the room’s fittings into the residence’s auroral timekeeping regimen.",
